<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Baleful" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Baleful,</orth> pernicious: <cit><quote>b. sorcery,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 1, 15</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>our b. enemies,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.122" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 122</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thou b. messenger,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.48" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 48</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>our b. news,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 1, 97</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. mistletoe,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 95</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>that b. burning night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.83" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 83</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. weeds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 2.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 3, 8</bibl></cit>.
